Company Overview of TMP Land Mortgage Fund Ltd



Snapshot People




Company Overview
TMP Land Mortgage Fund, Ltd. was dissolved in December 2004. Previously, the company offered short-term loans to unaffiliated parties secured by first deeds of trust on unimproved real properties primarily in the Inland Empire area of southern California. TMP Land Mortgage Fund was founded in 1991.


